00:34:23,907 --> 00:34:26,462

377
00:34:27,706 --> 00:34:29,983
Unbelievable!

378
00:34:33,888 --> 00:34:36,348
Chief Editor of the Hanju Daily!

379
00:34:36,348 --> 00:34:37,974
Yes, Madam?

380
00:34:38,782 --> 00:34:41,599
Chief Editor Choi Hee Joong!

381
00:34:45,488 --> 00:34:49,525
