- Did you study abroad on a scholarship from the Sungjin Group

382
00:34:49,525 --> 00:34:52,098
so you could drink all night?

383
00:34:52,098 --> 00:34:54,763
Your lack of sober judgment makes me think

384
00:34:54,763 --> 00:34:57,319
it's time for you to quit.

385
00:34:57,319 --> 00:35:00,520
How dare you do something like this without my consent?

386
00:35:00,520 --> 00:35:03,598
I'm sorry, Madam. Please forgive me.

387
00:35:04,721 --> 00:35:06,348
A daughter-in-law is nothing!

388
00:35:06,348 --> 00:35:10,440
She's family only as long as she's married to my son!

389
00:35:17,410 --> 00:35:20,150

390
00:35:51,192 --> 00:35:53,530
How is the investigation into Sungjin Bio going?

391
00:35:53,530 --> 00:35:57,397
Mr. Kim, the VP of Strategy is going to take the fall.

392
00:36:00,231 --> 00:36:04,788
It's a sad fate to be a prosecutor in this country, isn't it?

393
00:36:06,518 --> 00:36:10,701
